    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        Is the roof inspection really free in Largo?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes - 100% free with no obligation to purchase any services. We believe that providing honest, thorough inspections at no cost is the best way to earn the trust of Largo homeowners.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-btn" aria-expanded="false" onclick="this.setAttribute('aria-expanded',this.getAttribute('aria-expanded')==='true'?'false':'true');this.nextElementSibling.classList.toggle('open')">
        How long does a roof inspection take in Largo?
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A1A1A" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Most Largo inspections take 45-60 minutes. Larger homes or tile roofs may require slightly more time. We are thorough and methodical - we check every component rather than doing a quick walk-over.</div></div>
